Global Solenoid-Operated Electric Pinch Valves Market Insights
Solenoid-Operated Electric Pinch Valves Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.0 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Solenoid-Operated Electric Pinch Valves Market Overview
The global market for solenoid-operated electric pinch valves is experiencing significant growth, driven by increasing demand across industries such as oil & gas, pharmaceuticals, and food processing. The market value is estimated to reach USD 2.6 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.1% from 2025 to 2030. This growth is primarily fueled by technological advancements in valve automation and the increasing need for precision control in fluid systems. The demand for more efficient, reliable, and easy-to-operate systems in industries handling viscous fluids is accelerating the adoption of solenoid-operated electric pinch valves globally. With expanding industrial sectors, the market outlook remains positive with a strong push for innovations in valve designs and materials.

